Hi Eva, the video in 2:00, if you are sink in the sands and want motorcycle to move, here's how to do it;

first get out of the bike
1. turn on the bike but don't ride it yet, hold standing.
2. now make it run into gear number 1 (you know there are 5 gears you can switch between them gradually)
3. then the bike will start to move slowly while you are walking with it (*important, do not ride it until you get out of the sands)
4. it will be more helpful if your partner pushes from the back of the bike (it makes it faster to move from the sands)

I'm yemeni by the way,
I've been in your situation several times and these steps helped me every time.
